data.description: 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath spacious design with expansive windows that bathe the open floor plan in sunshine, highlighting the electric linear fireplace and cathedral ceilings. The eat-in island Kitchen is complete with ample counter space, stainless steel appliances with gas stove, and a dining area perfect for gatherings. The finished Lower Level includes daylight windows & egress. 2nd Floor Laundry Room is close & convenient to bedrooms. Owner’s Suite has a walk-in closet, ¾ shower, and a dual vanity. All appliances stay. Expansive fully fenced yard and huge non-buildable outlot to the east make this property a little chunk of paradise in the perfect Papillion location near the 370 corridor. 2.8% assumable rate for qualified buyers.
